---
import ContentLayout from "../layouts/ContentLayout.astro";
---

<ContentLayout
    title="Academy of Scholars"
    description="Green Schools Foundation sponsors the Academy of Scholars, recognizing students who have achieved academic excellence at Green High School and Green Middle School."
    showBreadcrumbs={true}
    breadcrumbs={[
        { name: "Foundation Initiatives", href: "/foundation-initiatives" },
        { name: "Academy of Scholars", href: "/academy-of-scholars" }
    ]}
>
    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Honoring Academic Excellence</h2>
        <p>
            Green Schools Foundation proudly sponsors the Academy of Scholars at Green High School and Green Middle School. This program recognizes students who have demonstrated outstanding academic achievement and commitment to their education.
        </p>
        <p>
            The Academy of Scholars honors our brightest students and encourages all students to strive for academic excellence. Being named to the Academy of Scholars is a significant achievement that reflects dedication, hard work, and a commitment to learning.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4">Academy of Scholars Recognition</h2>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div>
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10.394 2.08a1 1 0 00-.788 0l-7 3a1 1 0 000 1.84L5.25 8.051a.999.999 0 01.356-.257l4-1.714a1 1 0 11.788 1.838L7.667 9.088l1.94.831a1 1 0 00.787 0l7-3a1 1 0 000-1.838l-7-3zM3.31 9.397L5 10.12v4.102a8.969 8.969 0 00-1.05-.174 1 1 0 01-.89-.89 11.115 11.115 0 01.25-3.762zM9.3 16.573A9.026 9.026 0 007 14.935v-3.957l1.818.78a3 3 0 002.364 0l5.508-2.361a11.026 11.026 0 01.25 3.762 1 1 0 01-.89.89 8.968 8.968 0 00-5.35 2.524 1 1 0 01-1.4 0zM6 18a1 1 0 001-1v-2.065a8.935 8.935 0 00-2-.712V17a1 1 0 001 1z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Green High School</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
                    The Green High School Academy of Scholars honors students who have achieved a <strong>3.5 GPA or higher</strong> for the previous school year.
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6 2a1 1 0 00-1 1v1H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2h-1V3a1 1 0 10-2 0v1H7V3a1 1 0 00-1-1zm0 5a1 1 0 000 2h8a1 1 0 100-2H6z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Recognition:</strong> Late October, annually</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M9 4.804A7.968 7.968 0 005.5 4c-1.255 0-2.443.29-3.5.804v10A7.969 7.969 0 015.5 14c1.669 0 3.218.51 4.5 1.385A7.962 7.962 0 0114.5 14c1.255 0 2.443.29 3.5.804v-10A7.968 7.968 0 0014.5 4c-1.255 0-2.443.29-3.5.804V12a1 1 0 11-2 0V4.804z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Green Middle School</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
                    Green Middle School honor students are recognized for their academic achievements and dedication to learning.
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6 2a1 1 0 00-1 1v1H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2h-1V3a1 1 0 10-2 0v1H7V3a1 1 0 00-1-1zm0 5a1 1 0 000 2h8a1 1 0 100-2H6z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Recognition:</strong> End of school year</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Program Benefits</h2>
        <div class="grid-3">
            <div class="text-center bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Recognition</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                    Students receive public recognition for their academic achievements at special ceremonies.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6 6V5a3 3 0 013-3h2a3 3 0 013 3v1h2a2 2 0 012 2v3.57A22.952 22.952 0 0110 13a22.95 22.95 0 01-8-1.43V8a2 2 0 012-2h2zm2-1a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v1H8V5zm1 5a1 1 0 011-1h.01a1 1 0 110 2H10a1 1 0 01-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        <path d="M2 13.692V16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2v-2.308A24.974 24.974 0 0110 15c-2.796 0-5.487-.46-8-1.308z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Achievement</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                    A distinction that students can proudly include on college applications and resumes.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-secondary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3zM6 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM16 18v-3a5.972 5.972 0 00-.75-2.906A3.005 3.005 0 0119 15v3h-3zM4.75 12.094A5.973 5.973 0 004 15v3H1v-3a3 3 0 013.75-2.906z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Community</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                    Join a community of academically motivated peers who share your commitment to excellence.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Requirements</h2>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6">
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-semibold mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">High School Students</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-700">Maintain a cumulative GPA of 3.5 or higher for the previous school year.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-semibold mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Middle School Students</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-700">Meet the honor roll requirements established by Green Middle School.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-semibold mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Good Standing</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-700">Be a student in good standing at Green Local Schools.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4">Why Academic Excellence Matters</h2>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">For Students</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Opens doors to scholarship opportunities</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Strengthens college and university applications</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Builds confidence and self-discipline</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Prepares for future career success</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">For Our Community</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Develops future leaders and contributors</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Strengthens our schools' reputation</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Inspires younger students to excel</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Creates a culture of achievement</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section text-center">
        <h2>Questions About Academy of Scholars?</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            For more information about the Academy of Scholars program, please contact Green Schools Foundation or speak with your school counselor.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:greenschoolsfoundation@gmail.com?subject=Academy of Scholars Inquiry" class="button-primary mr-4">
            Contact Us
        </a>
        <a href="/foundation-initiatives" class="button-secondary">
            View All Initiatives
        </a>
    </div>
</ContentLayout>
